  
                Constructors                                                               Methods
  
  1. Initialize state of object                                              1. Expose behavior of the object
  
  2. Invoked implicitly(by system)                                           2. Invoked explicitly(by user)
  
  3. Constructor name should be same as class name                           3. Method name can be different depending upon the user
  
  4. No return type                                                          4. Method must have return type
  
  5. Compiler provides default constructor                                   5. Compiler does not provide default method
  
